https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/FISHEYE035/Configuring+Commit+Hooks#Configuringcommithooks-Perforce

The syntax for the example perforce trigger is incorrect, double-quotes within the p4 trigger command have to be replaced with {{%quote%}}.

The supplied example reads:

{noformat}
trigger-04 change-commit //... "/usr/bin/curl -s -o /dev/null -X POST -H "X-Api-Key: abcdefg123456" -H "Content-Type: application/json" http://atlas:8060/fecru/rest-service-fecru/admin/repositories-v1/perforce_widget/scan
{noformat}

when in fact it should look like:

{noformat}
trigger-04 change-commit //... "/usr/bin/curl -s -o /dev/null -X POST -H %quote%X-Api-Key:abcdefg123456%quote% -H %quote%Content-Type: application/json%quote% -m 20 http://atlas:8060/fecru/rest-service-fecru/admin/repositories-v1/perforce_widget/scan"
{noformat}

